# Sessions Content

## Session 1

- `#include` Preprocessor Directive
- `iostream` Header File and its Object `cout` and Manipulator `endl`
- `using` directive
- `std` Namespace
- `main` Function
- Escape Sequence Character `\n`
- White Space
- `Hello World!` Program

## Session 2

- Variables
- Data Types and their ranges
- Name Convention
- Stream Operators
- Arithmetic Operators
- Type Conversion
- Unary Arithmetic Operators
- Conditional Statements
    - `return` Statement with Conditions
- Comparison or Relational operators
- `cin` Object
- Logical or Boolean Operators
- Assignments Operators
- Ternary Conditional Operators
